				<li class="comment-author">
				
				
				
					<div class="profile" >
						
							






    <img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2011/10/05/AnnieMouse/59d44d03-8920-490b-a4e9-268f5c35648d/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />



