					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>Forward planning  works wonders:  before you go out get two really large glasses of water and a tube of Berocca vitamin B fizzers (or equivalent) and put them next to your bed.  When you get home drop a fizzer in one glass, drink the water, drink the dissolved fizzer, pass out.  You will be amazed how human you feel when you wake up.</p>
						
					</div>
